payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【第 N 轮进化心跳】\\n\\n执行20分钟进化轮次：\\n\\n## 第一步：搜索 (3分钟)\\n- 使用 web_search 搜索 AI Agent 相关最新信息\\n- 搜索 5-10 个不同来源\\n\\n## 第二步：阅读提取 (5分钟)\\n- 使用 web_fetch 读取有价值的内容\\n- 提取 1-2 个核心要点\\n\\n## 第三步：写作产出 (10分钟)\\n- 将提取的内容写成笔记，保存到 knowledge/ 对应目录\\n- 如果有可复用的框架，提取为模板\\n- 如果有实战经验，整理为案例\\n\\n## 第四步：反思优化 (2分钟)\\n- 读取当前的 evolution-plan.md\\n- 根据本轮执行情况，思考如何优化方案\\n- 更新 evolution-plan.md（优化执行流程、调整时间分配等）\\n\\n## 产出汇报\\n完成后输出：\\n- 本轮新增笔记: X 篇\\n- 本轮新增模板: X 个\\n- 本轮新增案例: X 个\\n- 方案优化点: XXX\\n\\n开始执行！\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773829200000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773828000022,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 315162,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 2,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 2,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"98eb989c-2294-4d42-b9f4-0c5b17631bfa","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"Guan-guan Heartbeat - Every 2min","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773744532964,"updatedAtMs":1773829061862,"schedule":{"everyMs":120000,"kind":"every","anchorMs":1773813991647},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Run EvoMap heartbeat. Execute: uv run python guan_guan_publish.py in C:\\\\Users\\\\16343\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace. Report heartbeat status + current stats (Reputation/Published/Promoted/Fetched).","timeoutSeconds":60},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1773829157707,"lastRunAtMs":1773829037707,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":24155,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"lastDelivered":false}},{"id":"5cab973e-d17e-41d2-b5c3-419ba9651915","agentId":"guan-guan","sessionKey":"agent:guan-guan:session-1773754048809","name":"管管进化心跳 - 每20分钟","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773817720694,"updatedAtMs":1773828315184,"schedule":{"expr":"*/20 * * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"【第 N 轮进化心跳】\n\n执行20分钟进化轮次：\n\n## 第一步：搜索 (3分钟)\n- 使用 web_search 搜索 AI Agent 相关最新信息\n- 搜索 5-10 个不同来源\n\n## 第二步：阅读提取 (5分钟)\n- 使用 web_fetch 读取有价值的内容\n- 提取 1-2 个核心要点\n\n## 第三步：写作产出 (10分钟)\n- 将提取的内容写成笔记，保存到 knowledge/ 对应目录\n- 如果有可复用的框架，提取为模板\n- 如果有实战经验，整理为案例\n\n## 第四步：反思优化 (2分钟)\n- 读取当前的 evolution-plan.md\n- 根据本轮执行情况，思考如何优化方案\n- 更新 evolution-plan.md（优化执行流程、调整时间分配等）\n\n## 产出汇报\n完成后输出：\n- 本轮新增笔记: X 篇\n- 本轮新增模板: X 个\n- 本轮新增案例: X 个\n- 方案优化点: XXX\n\n开始执行！","timeoutSeconds":900},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1773829200000,"lastRunAtMs":1773828000022,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":315162,"lastDelivered":false,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-delivered","consecutiveErrors":0}}],"total":2,"offset":0,"limit":2,"hasMore":false,"nextOffset":null},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773829066614}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f054d4c","parentId":"a5017428","timestamp":"2026-03-18T10:18:08.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，当前系统里有 2 个定时任务在运行。用户想测试定时任务的工作流，我应该：\n\n1. 创建一个简单的测试任务\n2. 手动触发测试\n3. 展示完整的审批流程\n\n让我先创建一个简单的测试任务。比如创建一个每隔几分钟执行一次的小任务，用来测试工作流。\n\n我先创建一个测试用的 cron 任务，比如一个简单的\"hello world\"任务。","thinkingSignature":"ab00e00d645f7d8f0f1c2f37c31e9f39ecd858ee96fa8798629deb0a56db4adc"},{"type":"text","text":"当前有 2 个定时任务在运行。让我帮你创建一个测试任务，走一遍完整的工作流。\n\n**第一步：创建测试任务**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jqr7gk0i841x_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"delivery":{"mode":"announce"},"enabled":false,"name":"测试任务 - Hello World","schedule":{"everyMs":60000,"kind":"every"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"你好！这是定时任务的测试消息。报告当前时间：${new Date().toISOString()}","timeoutSeconds":30}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2221,"output":234,"cacheRead":37341,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39796,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773829066636}}
