{"type":"message","id":"20e76a3c","parentId":"9ec508af","timestamp":"2026-03-18T10:18:32.413Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_76tmexyr4azi_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"98eb989c-2294-4d42-b9f4-0c5b17631bfa\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Guan-guan Heartbeat - Every 2min\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773744532964,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773829061862,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"everyMs\": 120000,\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"anchorMs\": 1773813991647\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run EvoMap heartbeat. Execute: uv run python guan_guan_publish.py in C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\16343\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace. Report heartbeat status + current stats (Reputation/Published/Promoted/Fetched).\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 60\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773829157707,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773829037707,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 24155,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"5cab973e-d17e-41d2-b5c3-419ba9651915\",\n      \"agentId\": \"guan-guan\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:guan-guan:session-1773754048809\",\n      \"name\": \"管管进化心跳 - 每20分钟\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773817720694,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773828315184,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"*/20 * * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【第 N 轮进化心跳】\\n\\n执行20分钟进化轮次：\\n\\n## 第一步：搜索 (3分钟)\\n- 使用 web_search 搜索 AI Agent 相关最新信息\\n- 搜索 5-10 个不同来源\\n\\n## 第二步：阅读提取 (5分钟)\\n- 使用 web_fetch 读取有价值的内容\\n- 提取 1-2 个核心要点\\n\\n## 第三步：写作产出 (10分钟)\\n- 将提取的内容写成笔记，保存到 knowledge/ 对应目录\\n- 如果有可复用的框架，提取为模板\\n- 如果有实战经验，整理为案例\\n\\n## 第四步：反思优化 (2分钟)\\n- 读取当前的 evolution-plan.md\\n- 根据本轮执行情况，思考如何优化方案\\n- 更新 evolution-plan.md（优化执行流程、调整时间分配等）\\n\\n## 产出汇报\\n完成后输出：\\n- 本轮新增笔记: X 篇\\n- 本轮新增模板: X 个\\n- 本轮新增案例: X 个\\n- 方案优化点: XXX\\n\\n开始执行！\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773829200000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773828000022,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 315162,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"379017ba-4bd7-47e0-8c50-91cf7af12241\",\n      \"agentId\": \"xiao-yi\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:xiao-yi:session-1773813212458\",\n      \"name\": \"进化方案执行与优化\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773813436659,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773826137552,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"*/15 * * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【定时进化任务 - 小报】\\n\\n执行快速进化检查：\\n\\n1. 统计当前知识库数量\\n2. 简短汇报学习进展（新增 X 篇）\\n3. 输出小报格式：\\n\\n---\\n🧚 小艺心跳小报\\n\\n## 学习进展\\n- 新增知识: X 篇\\n- 知识库总计: Y 篇\\n\\n## 状态\\n- 心跳时间: {时间}\\n---\\n\\n（每15分钟执行一次，简洁汇报）\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773825590635,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 8984,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"9bcafe28-8f88-40ad-adee-f24e521f2926\",\n      \"agentId\": \"xiao-yi\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:xiao-yi:cron:379017ba-4bd7-47e0-8c50-91cf7af12241\",\n      \"name\": \"小艺进化汇总 - 每2小时\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773814778672,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773826137512,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"0 */2 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【定时进化任务 - 2小时汇总】\\n\\n执行完整进化检查并生成汇总报告：\\n\\n1. 统计知识库当前数量\\n2. 梳理本周期学习内容\\n3. 生成汇总报告格式：\\n\\n---\\n## 📊 进化报表 - {时间}\\n\\n### 学习成果\\n- 学习篇数：X\\n- 主要内容：技术/审美/工具/人格/认知/社交\\n- 新技能：\\n\\n### 方案优化\\n- 调整内容：\\n- 优化建议：\\n\\n### 下一步计划\\n-\\n---\\n\\n（每2小时执行一次，详细汇报）\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"to\": \"gateway-client\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773821265251,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 78086,\n        \"lastError\": \"AxiosError: Request failed with status code 400\",\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"9ccb5346-aecd-4d9d-b10b-e8c946c6e80e\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:session-1773829037775\",\n      \"name\": \"测试任务 - Hello World\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773829088657,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773829098802,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"everyMs\": 60000,\n